Name:         Mimic Octopus
Scientific:   Thaumoctopus mimicus
Class:        Cephalopoda
Habitat:      Shallow sea
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     1 years
Weight:       0.5 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Can mimic 15+ different species including lionfish and flatfish

Name:         Blue Whale
Scientific:   Balaenoptera musculus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore (krill)
Lifespan:     80 years
Weight:       150000 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Largest animal ever known; heart is size of a small car

Name:         Cheetah
Scientific:   Acinonyx jubatus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     12 years
Weight:       65 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Fastest land animal at 120 km/h; cannot roar; purrs instead

